     C*
     C*    SETON U6 FOR CL MESSAGE AND END IF PASSWORD CHANGE
     C*      FACILITY NOT USED
     C*
     C           BJPCFU    IFNE 'Y'
     C                     SETON                       LRU6
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
     C*
     C*   DATE FORMAT CHECK
     C*
     C           BJDFIN    IFEQ 'M'
     C                     SETON                     98
     C                     END
     C*
     C*   RUN DATE CHECK
     C*
     C                     MOVE BJMRDT    SRUNA
     C*
     C*   CHECK LAST PASSWORD CHANGE DATE AND TIME
     C*
     C           LPWD      IFEQ 0
     C           LPWT      ANDEQ*BLANKS
     C                     SETON                     30
     C                     ELSE
     C*
     C* CONVERT DATE
     C*
     C                     MOVE LPWD      ZDAYNO
     C                     EXSR ZDATE2
     C                     MOVE ZADATE    SLUPWD
     C                     MOVE LPWT      SLUPWT
     C                     END
     C**
     C**  MAIN PROCESSING
     C**
     C           TAG01     TAG                             **** TAG01 ****
     C                     Z-ADD0         Z       20
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ERCD
     C                     MOVEA'0000'    *IN,20
     C                     MOVE '0'       *IN28
     C**
     C** LOOP UNTIL A CORRECT USER PROFILE IS ENTERED
     C**
     C           *IN20     DOUEQ'0'
     C                     WRITESF0210F1
     C**
     C*    READ WORKSTATION FILE / HELP FACILITY
     C**
     C**         *IN19     DOUEQ'0'                                       S01199
     C                     READ SF0210F1                 19
     C**         *IN19     IFEQ '1'                                       S01199
     C**                   MOVEAERR       HERCD 160                       S01199
     C**                   MOVEL'SF0210  'HBPGM   6                       S01199
     C**                   CALL 'MHELP'                                   S01199
     C**                   PARM           HBPGM                           S01199
     C**                   PARM           HERCD                           S01199
     C**                   END                                            S01199
     C**                   END                                            S01199
     C**
     C** IF F3 PRESSED, EXIT
     C**
     C           *INKC     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
     C**
     C**  INITIALISE FIELDS AND INDICATORS
     C**
     C                     SETOF                     20
     C                     Z-ADD0         Z       20
     C                     MOVE *BLANKS   ERCD
     C                     MOVEA'0000'    *IN,20
     C                     MOVE '0'       *IN28
     C**
     C           SUSRC     IFNE *BLANKS
     C**
     C** CHECK SUSRC IS LEFT ADJUSTED
     C**
     C                     MOVELSUSRC     CHK     1
     C           CHK       IFEQ ' '
     C                     SETON                     20
     C                     ADD  1         Z
     C                     MOVE '001'     ERR,Z
     C                     GOTO TAG02
     C                     END
     C**
     C** CHECK SUSRC CONTAINS NO EMBEDDED BLANKS
     C**
