     C           X         DOWLE10
     C           CHK1,X    IFNE ' '
     C           *IN28     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     20
     C                     ADD  1         Z
     C                     MOVE '002'     ERR,Z
     C                     GOTO TAG02
     C                     END
     C**
     C                     ELSE
     C                     SETON                     28
     C                     END
     C**
     C                     ADD  1         X
     C                     END
     C**
     C**  GET USER DETAILS FORM LF/MUSER
